data.description: Peaceful country home on .95 acres. This 1862 square foot, 3 bedroom and 3 bath house is ready for your personal touches. There is a spacious kitchen adjacent to the dining room as well as a large living room with wood burning fireplace. Downstairs includes large bonus room with pellet stove and bar, bathroom with walk-in shower and laundry room. Fully fenced yard with garden, trees and lots of room for entertaining. Newer roof, windows and septic tank.
